messages.message:
Hi. Do we have any data or testing to support an answer the question - How does the length of the document impact the accuracy and processing speed within AI Hub Build?
> For context, this is a JPMC team looking to potentially leverage AI Hub Build for agreement documents (hundreds of pages), but concerned it's designed to process such longer documents.
I did some calculation on large doc and cam out with an average of 5 seconds a page for processing time.
